## [PageBreak](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break)

### Methods

|                                                           Method                                                           |                                            Return type                                             |                                                           Brief description                                                            |
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| [copy()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#copy())                                   | [PageBreak](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break)               | Returns a detached, deep copy of the current element.                                                                                  |
| [getAttributes()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#getAttributes())                 | `Object`                                                                                           | Retrieves the element's attributes.                                                                                                    |
| [getNextSibling()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#getNextSibling())               | [Element](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/element)                    | Retrieves the element's next sibling element.                                                                                          |
| [getParent()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#getParent())                         | [ContainerElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/container-element) | Retrieves the element's parent element.                                                                                                |
| [getPreviousSibling()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#getPreviousSibling())       | [Element](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/element)                    | Retrieves the element's previous sibling element.                                                                                      |
| [getType()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#getType())                             | [ElementType](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/element-type)           | Retrieves the element's [ElementType](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/element-type).                      |
| [isAtDocumentEnd()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#isAtDocumentEnd())             | `Boolean`                                                                                          | Determines whether the element is at the end of the [Document](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/document). |
| [removeFromParent()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#removeFromParent())           | [PageBreak](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break)               | Removes the element from its parent.                                                                                                   |
| [setAttributes(attributes)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break#setAttributes(Object)) | [PageBreak](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/document/page-break)               | Sets the element's attributes.                                                                                                         |
